This folder contains the custom codes applied to assess the findings of the study \expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
entitled "Thalamic regulation of reinforcement learning strategies across prefrontal-striatal networks\'94, which was published in Nature Communications.\
\
It includes the following sub-folders: \
(1)Behaviour: the codes used to analyse the behaviour data and save the onset of the events that used for the GLM analyses. \
(2)GLM: the codes used to perform the GLMs of the fMRI data based on the SPM toolbox\
(3)DCM: the codes used to perform the DCM analyses of the fMRI data based on the SPM toolbox\
(4)RSA: the codes used to perform the RSA analyses of the fMRI data based on both SPM and RSA toolbox\
(5)PPI: the codes used to perform the PPI analyses of the fMRI data based on both SPM and gPPI toolbox\
