- The key requirement is the installation of MATLAB (produced by The MathWorks, Inc.\
Natick, MA, USA. http://www.mathworks.com/). \
\
To successfully run the codes, some other toolbox are required: (1) SPM12 (Wellcome Department of Imaging Neuroscience, University College London, UK; http://www.fil.ion.ucl.ac.uk/spm) for the GLM and DCM analyses of fMRI data. \
(2) RSA toolbox (https://github.com/rsagroup/rsatoolbox) for the RSA analysis of fMRI data\
(3) gPPI toolbox (https://www.nitrc.org/projects/gppi) for the psychophysiology interaction analysis of fMRI data\
\
